Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we haven't mentioned so far, we said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,truth only comes, meaning only comes out of context.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And one context that we haven't spoken about this morning, of course, is karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That you have both discernible context, undiscernible context,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and non-identifiable context called karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why much scientific experimentation doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so they come up with contradictory results because they don't define the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason computers can never create an artificial intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it can only do logic trees, logic trees in human intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:01:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Human intelligence is a subjective evaluation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of an infinite number of millions of data of information
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which it intuitively wins its way through without actually processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do a computer replica of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is for one thing, the major portion of the context is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only program content.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One piece of context that is not available to put on the computer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's unknown, is karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which is in the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So all you could put on the computer would be that which is reasonably logically recallable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It totally, you cannot put what's in the unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,because by definition it's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's unconscious, it is not available data.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't put that in the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Context is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Computers only deal with the linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, meaning, significance, value,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't put Mother's Day on a computer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because the reverence,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you put reverence into a computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Logic series, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's a feeling state, it's a way of being with,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a way of being with the totality of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and the totality of the feminine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The way this consciousness is with the feminine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,evolved over eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolved over eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's reverence for the feminine is eons old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That cannot be put into a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's context that gives the thing meaning and value,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our spiritual work then derives its power,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,derives its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We said you can go to metaphysical lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for 35 years and never change one iota.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the person has denied the power within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the power to transform the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the world of the word,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,into the world of the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Into the subjective experiential world of spiritual truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The power is within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does the power come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The power comes from willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There was the willingness to accept that women were to be revered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandparents said that, my father said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no resistance to that, no resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth instantly at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There was trust in the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There was trust in the sincerity with which they were said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There was trust in the integrity of the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of love for the source of the information,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,all resistance was relinquished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was accepted as truth and incorporated within for a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Same thing should then ideally happen with spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:05:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The educator should be sufficient that one's trust in it is profound like it was in my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the resistance dissolves itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell you that the feminine is infinitely divine, worshipful as the expression of God
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in that expression, you know that's the truth, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You reverence that within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The feminine within yourself you reverence as the expression of God, as it expresses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,itself in the feminine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As it comes out of form, the divine begins to take on attributes which we eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize as form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference between male and female, divinity has already come into form as male and female,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,because tomorrow is Mother's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concentrating on the feminine, the magnificence and the beauty of divinity as expressed as
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the feminine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So our acceptance of that doesn't depend on its being accepted by other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference to me how other people hold women within their psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no conflict and no problem with the way it is within.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As close to its being, as close to its divine nature as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So what did the grandparents do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle, my, all the men in the family held women who reverenced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was it so powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because they were holding it as close to its divine origination as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They were holding it as a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as your uncle, I mean, not as your aunt or your grandmother or your mother, as personages,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but they were holding it as a powerful field of realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I got what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I got what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity innate within the feminine, that's what I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it is worthy of reverence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So our resistance to incorporating truth and resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to incorporating truth and instantly recognizing it then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the resistance to it can be bypassed by faith, love, the trust and openness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the divinity that we intuit as the field out of which the information is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It is out of infinite love that that is forthcoming from consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness into the awareness of the listener.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't take 35 years of attending lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes one instant of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One instant of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,One reason we use kinesiology is to clear the obstacles to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell you that the expression of motherhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and this calibrates at 540,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way women are held by political positions,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way women are held within the urbic world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if we calibrate those levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that sort of removes the doubtfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the doubtingness of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect is the great doubter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the great blocker to truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So we try to also handle the ego at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So all that I've ever spoken of became an absolute reality in one instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,35 years ago or whatever it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in the long distant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All that I'm saying today became an instant reality, wordlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what speaks right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:10:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What speaks right now searches for how to express that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so as to bypass the resistance of the intellect, the mind, and the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, as I saw as a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the incredible,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,magnificent sense of the divinity of woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One instant, my grandfather said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll never speak to your grandmother that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I got how she was held.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So it takes one instant to get what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not 35 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It only takes one instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In one instant, the ego lets go its resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,out of faith, confidence, and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When my father said that to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was not a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So all resistance stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that became incorporated into the truth of my own reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of my own reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to use personal experience to demonstrate a certain principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing I want to happen is people come to these lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and then tell me nothing has changed and nothing's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In a dead body, I killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I went to all these lectures and nothing changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to die and it's going to be on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the you made me do it game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in a certain context then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that I belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I'm saying today belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody here totally owns what's being said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody here totally owns the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the speaker then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The speaker is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual educator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that for a term?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a good term?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual educator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we share with you the truth that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it was subjectively experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and as it is present within.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not comprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we go back to what it is that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,keeps it from being comprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We try to explain it in terms that are
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,understandable to the scientifically trained mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus wasn't dealing with scientifically trained people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't read or write for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a snap of a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They hadn't read all the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There weren't any books on the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have evolved in the last couple thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the listener, the student of today,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is somewhat different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Considerably different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Far more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people there that Jesus dealt with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,were probably in the 200s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That became followers were below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was the power of the truth coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that transformed the people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people instantly saw
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth that he revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was his authority
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which they became enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The saints were all became enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result of the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to drop all resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and just respond to that truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I did with my grandparents
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and my father
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,about who women really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got in an instant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who they really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't need to read any books on the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just got it right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One instant I got who women were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the lectures all we want
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is in one instant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we get who we really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us here are a gift to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if we're a gift to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a gift to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So our being here at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,all of us who are here at this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,are collectively a gift to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The world calibrates at 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This group calibrates at 430
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,as they walked in the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's already a gift to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of just who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you are is a gift to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Different way to hold yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When you walk through Walmarts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and you smile at somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,they get it as a gift to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice how they light up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever walk through Walmarts and smile at people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody lights up all the way down the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you probably never noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pushing this and you're pushing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You look over and smile at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It knocks them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so happy that somebody smiles at her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and recognizes her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that she just beams right back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like instant love all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to do that in the streets of New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The streets of New York City are like Walmarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just walk down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and just love everybody as they came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,People just beamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop anybody on the street of New York
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and start talking about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you think about me or so and so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll instantly give you a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you've known each other for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no barrier there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the streets of the city of New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's a character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The dialect, the whole style,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what it means to be a New Yorker,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the certain implicit understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of the rights and wrongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Under certain circumstances, stealing is not really stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He left it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He left it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, if he left it out, that's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Change of context.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He left it laying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay, he left it laying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a judge wouldn't convict you, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He left it laying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He left it laying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole different context of ethics and morality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is acceptable there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is not acceptable here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The context of New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is different than the context of elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The context makes it different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The context makes its meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and its significance become different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So context defines meaning and significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To do the same thing here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be nothing at all in New York
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,would be ethically a different animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A different animal altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He just can't take his change
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and not feel guilty about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he left all his change on the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be there when you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the great block?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the great block to keep it from sinking in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried to approach it from the viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that the ego as a totality
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,will not tolerate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,any infringement of its boundaries
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because it realizes that it's a threat to its totality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an interlocking system
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and to let in love
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,means that the end is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To allow in love
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,means to the ego ultimate dissolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all else then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ego fears love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is scared to death of Mother's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is scared to death
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of what Mother's Day really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scared to death
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of what Mother's Day really is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,really is, really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The recognition of the divinity of love
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in its expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of course on Mother's Day as the feminine,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,would mean that love
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as a prevailing dominant value
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,would infiltrate all of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be the end
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of many corporations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and political positions and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego is scared to death of Mother's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's scared of Father's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wait till June.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So love then becomes the greatest threat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to not go to 35 years of lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is nothing happening then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret of it is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret is love for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret of it is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,faith and confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and the integrity of the source of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And one means of accomplishing that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is by kinesiologic testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To what degree you can trust
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the validity of what is being said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes through the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated energy field of the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of the truth then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth because truth is only meaningful
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,within a certain context.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the context of the words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that have been said?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We could test the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of Deutschland über alles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we could test the context
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which it came,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of Adolf Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Adolf Hitler played upon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of fascism in Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,arose out of a philosophic position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in my book, I forget his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfaffenhofer or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They justified the German invasion by...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a doctrine of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Räumsleben or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lebensraum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That Germany had the right to invade
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,neighboring countries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because it needed room to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, that was a weak one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it built the whole country.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole structure came out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Room to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Golly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I transmit
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fellow drivers on the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I need room to drive, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I have the right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to crash my car into his
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and knock him off the road
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because I need driving room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a rather weak intellectual position,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we ever calibrate that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.99,0:22:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Deutschland über alles
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates over 100, 110,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,120, 130, 140, 140.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf Hitler at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:23:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate over 120, 130, 140, 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It corresponded, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.91,0:23:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.91,0:23:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So then the demagogue finds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the downside in human nature
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and knows how to directly appeal to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The smart politician knows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what the consciousness level of mankind is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and that he can easily summon up that hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows that hatred is there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,only waiting to be summoned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,At the opposite end,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we know in spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the reality of existence itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that the capacity for love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and for enlightenment is also available
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,within human mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll leave hatred to other people
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to summon that forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And all we want to recognize here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.00,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is that divinity is the source of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is out of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that consciousness arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It is consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is the field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,holding us all together,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which everybody is able to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and experience that which is being said.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.05,0:24:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence within all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is what allows us
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.16,0:24:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.85,0:24:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the subjective experience
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which we are
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.22,0:24:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and which we're trying to verbalize here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So reality then is a radical subjectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.24,0:24:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get to a lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.24,0:24:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,on meditative techniques at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.24,0:24:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But at all times,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.61,0:24:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the shortcut to God is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.61,0:24:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to merely realize
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite presence
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.02,0:24:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.31,0:24:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.74,0:25:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the source
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.14,0:25:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has within it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.39,0:25:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.39,0:25:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to create its own existence
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.39,0:25:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,out of what comes existence itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.77,0:25:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We bypass causality
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.77,0:25:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as a plausible explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.82,0:25:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think in the first lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.82,0:25:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we knocked causality on its butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.82,0:25:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the world hasn't heard of that yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.82,0:25:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but the days of causality
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.82,0:25:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,are over, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.82,0:25:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.82,0:25:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the ego will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.99,0:25:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,well, what about causality
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.15,0:25:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,as an explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.15,0:25:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is created
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.15,0:25:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in such a way
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.48,0:25:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that its essence
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.86,0:25:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolds
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.86,0:25:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.33,0:25:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of its source.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.33,0:26:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of the divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.33,0:26:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of the source of creation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.33,0:26:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that all things are perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.33,0:26:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what they are at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.33,0:26:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That which appears catastrophically awful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.88,0:26:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,appears that way
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.88,0:26:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's out of context.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.25,0:26:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.25,0:26:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in the present,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.65,0:26:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that looks terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.65,0:26:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.65,0:26:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's already a judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.65,0:26:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The awful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.53,0:26:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,manifesting its awfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.53,0:26:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is supposed to be awful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.53,0:26:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in the awfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.53,0:26:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of its awfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.93,0:26:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's perfectly awful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.93,0:26:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in the dreadfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.93,0:26:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of its horrific
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.98,0:26:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.24,0:26:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.43,0:26:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.95,0:26:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to be that way, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.95,0:26:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.95,0:26:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.95,0:27:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, we choose differently this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.95,0:27:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We look at the dead bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.95,0:27:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.95,0:27:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we look at the run over children,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.18,0:27:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and something within us begins to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.26,0:27:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But it changes so slowly, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.26,0:27:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you calibrate yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.26,0:27:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness level of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.26,0:27:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,century by century by century,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.26,0:27:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,190, 190 you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.26,0:27:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, didn't mankind learn anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.26,0:27:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,War of 1812?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.40,0:27:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One war right after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.23,0:27:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler was really so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.23,0:27:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he was really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.45,0:27:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Napoleon had just pulled that trick
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.45,0:27:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and blown it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.45,0:27:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And he went around and did the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.45,0:27:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Invade Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.53,0:27:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,East and west are from the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.53,0:27:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can anybody be so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.53,0:27:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.15,0:27:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So that ignorance and that stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.15,0:27:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we're trying to find a way through today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.15,0:27:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha and Jesus both said,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.40,0:27:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the only sin is that of ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.40,0:27:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sin as a moralistic put down
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.40,0:28:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is really useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.02,0:28:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's using guilt as a hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.02,0:28:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to beat people to death with
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.02,0:28:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or beat yourself to death with.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It says there is ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.22,0:28:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorance seems to be innate then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.90,0:28:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in the structure of the ego itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.90,0:28:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you go to 35 years of lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.90,0:28:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and not get anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.90,0:28:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Still be the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.90,0:28:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something within
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.95,0:28:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego itself
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.95,0:28:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that accounts for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.07,0:28:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Century after century.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.07,0:28:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Millions slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.07,0:28:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to the next century.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.07,0:28:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be better? You'd think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.07,0:28:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, still 190. Millions more slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.07,0:28:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Still 190. Millions more slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.07,0:28:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, whoa, there's something
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.81,0:28:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that's really thick-headed about the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.81,0:28:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some innate stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.81,0:28:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Innate stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.81,0:28:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There we got it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.16,0:29:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.96,0:29:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.92,0:29:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So we should treat it like an imbecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.92,0:29:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.02,0:29:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb. Pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.60,0:29:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We should feel sorry for the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.70,0:29:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.96,0:29:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It can sit there for 35 years
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.96,0:29:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and not get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.69,0:29:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think maybe what happened was...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.00,0:29:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I see what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.22,0:29:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.44,0:29:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. The source
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.44,0:29:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,from which you are learning
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.52,0:29:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,or hearing or something
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.52,0:29:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,has to be of a certain dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.52,0:29:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To break through the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.52,0:29:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I held my grandfathers
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.51,0:29:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with reverence and respect
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.51,0:29:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and my father and my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.51,0:29:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.82,0:29:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.82,0:29:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.91,0:30:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The way women were treated
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.91,0:30:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,was appropriate to the way
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.91,0:30:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that they were held.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.91,0:30:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And they showed me how they were held.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.32,0:30:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason it rang true
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.32,0:30:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is because it was based on spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.35,0:30:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the feminine is the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.35,0:30:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.38,0:30:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In that genre
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.38,0:30:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of human expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.48,0:30:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got it in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.01,0:30:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing should happen
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.81,0:30:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in any spiritual literature,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.81,0:30:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teaching, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.31,0:30:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The respect, the letting go of resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.31,0:30:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.08,0:30:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of its source.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.89,0:30:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the source of its truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.89,0:30:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of its truth
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.61,0:30:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.61,0:30:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,within
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.61,0:30:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.17,0:30:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Classically with speaking now
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.22,0:30:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be called
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.22,0:30:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in Sanskrit
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.22,0:31:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Purusha.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.22,0:31:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Purusha would be the essence
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.22,0:31:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of the self
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.55,0:31:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.55,0:31:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,which is expressing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.55,0:31:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.55,0:31:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is expressing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.55,0:31:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.94,0:31:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with the body
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.94,0:31:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is using at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.94,0:31:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It will use anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.20,0:31:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't trust Purusha.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.20,0:31:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It will grab anybody, speak to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.29,0:31:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.01,0:31:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.01,0:31:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.01,0:31:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of the truth of all spiritual teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.01,0:31:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.18,0:31:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,self within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.66,0:31:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.66,0:31:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the power
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.06,0:31:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.46,0:31:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only the recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.46,0:31:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if what my grandparents
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.76,0:31:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,had told me, my grandfathers
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.76,0:31:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,my uncle
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.85,0:32:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.85,0:32:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,was not innately true.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.85,0:32:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It would not have resonated within.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.46,0:32:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.46,0:32:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of truth within me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.46,0:32:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was capable
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.50,0:32:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of hearing the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.50,0:32:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only because of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.50,0:32:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of truth within
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.50,0:32:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.50,0:32:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is any capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.50,0:32:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to extract any truth
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.55,0:32:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the research that we've
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.23,0:32:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,done and we are sharing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.42,0:32:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.42,0:32:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.42,0:32:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a byproduct
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.42,0:32:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of the spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.42,0:32:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,entering a dense matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.42,0:32:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.42,0:32:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.42,0:32:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.01,0:32:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got enough questions
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.01,0:32:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep us busy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.08,0:32:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Each question reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.08,0:32:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what we intend to talk about anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.08,0:33:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and it just reminds me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.08,0:33:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of what we were going to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.70,0:33:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The disassembly of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.70,0:33:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,takes eons of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.70,0:33:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people in this audience
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.40,0:33:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,have been here 50, 60 times
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.40,0:33:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,before to try to accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.18,0:33:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that which
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.18,0:33:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,happens within an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.18,0:33:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I use the word happens
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.18,0:33:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,linguistically to make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.18,0:33:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To sense
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.19,0:33:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,one's reality is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.19,0:33:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.25,0:33:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.25,0:33:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look over here, you're looking
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.96,0:33:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,at the written word.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.96,0:33:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,35 years of the written word.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.30,0:33:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.75,0:33:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.72,0:33:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can all sense
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.72,0:34:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,right in this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.06,0:34:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.06,0:34:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are already distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.25,0:34:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.51,0:34:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.78,0:34:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you catch
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.78,0:34:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.78,0:34:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.09,0:34:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,just prior to the mind's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.09,0:34:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,commentary about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.21,0:34:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you back off from the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.21,0:34:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find an inner stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.94,0:34:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which hasn't said anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.26,0:34:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You live in the space
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.26,0:34:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,before the world has said anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.26,0:34:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When you walk outside
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.82,0:34:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you're struck by the beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.82,0:34:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of the surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.82,0:34:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't said anything about it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.36,0:34:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You live in that space.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.57,0:34:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The space is pre-verbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.57,0:34:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to mentalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.96,0:34:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty with
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.69,0:35:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,verbalization
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.78,0:35:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.53,0:35:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,one has to come out of that space
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.53,0:35:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and come forward into that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.55,0:35:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,verbalization because that's what
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.55,0:35:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the world expects.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.15,0:35:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.15,0:35:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,world speak
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.15,0:35:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or the world doesn't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.15,0:35:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because nothing is being spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.94,0:35:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right at this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.09,0:35:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,just sense within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.23,0:35:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that which hasn't had a second yet
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.23,0:35:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to make any comment about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.23,0:35:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,what the speaker is saying yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.69,0:35:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind's commentary
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.69,0:35:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is a delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.86,0:35:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a split second delay
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.86,0:35:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and you live in that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.86,0:35:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,before any comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.53,0:35:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When you dive off a diving board
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.53,0:35:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no thinkingness about it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:35:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as you hit the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.61,0:36:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The thinkingness comes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.61,0:36:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A split second later
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.61,0:36:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that dive wasn't made correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.61,0:36:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.61,0:36:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That dive wasn't made correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.61,0:36:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's a split second
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.61,0:36:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,after you go splat on the water
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.61,0:36:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.84,0:36:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that full gainer
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.84,0:36:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,was only a three-quarter gainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.94,0:36:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Valley Express
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.94,0:36:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,even as you think
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.96,0:36:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not getting it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.96,0:36:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you're there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.40,0:36:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now within everybody's consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.40,0:36:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.50,0:36:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.03,0:36:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,prior to any kind of content.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.03,0:36:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.46,0:36:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you draw back and you live
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.46,0:36:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in the space
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.61,0:36:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,right before the mind starts to make commentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.61,0:36:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you hold back
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.48,0:37:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in this space
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.86,0:37:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond the mind's thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.86,0:37:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkingness should be
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.82,0:37:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,voluntary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.40,0:37:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think when I'm forced to think
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.40,0:37:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the world is forever asking you to think
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.40,0:37:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.40,0:37:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.40,0:37:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.34,0:37:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,by coming out of the infinite peace
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.34,0:37:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and beauty of silence
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.09,0:37:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because the world has some
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.09,0:37:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,dumbbell question.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.78,0:37:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.26,0:37:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.26,0:37:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.26,0:37:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a new
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.59,0:37:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderful telephone
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.59,0:37:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.59,0:37:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a space phone
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.75,0:37:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever they call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.75,0:37:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand electronics and all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.75,0:37:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.07,0:37:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've got to read all this fine writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.07,0:37:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you buy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.32,0:37:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's got a 16-page manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.32,0:38:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.32,0:38:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite radio
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.32,0:38:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the waiting room of my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.32,0:38:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the radio I grew up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.32,0:38:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a dial.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.32,0:38:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes on, volume, off
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.55,0:38:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.55,0:38:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The world hates
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.55,0:38:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of a radio, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.55,0:38:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.57,0:38:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, somebody gave me an electronic
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.57,0:38:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,radio, a new radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.57,0:38:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a 14-page
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.57,0:38:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.57,0:38:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,get it to tell time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.57,0:38:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got one. I don't know what
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.86,0:38:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you do to make it even tell time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.61,0:38:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.61,0:38:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You get dragged into this complexity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.61,0:38:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It pulls all your energy and your interest
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.61,0:38:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and your survival gets pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.61,0:38:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.67,0:38:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Ramana Maharshi said it correctly
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.67,0:38:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,when I read Ramana Maharshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.67,0:38:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.73,0:38:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind gets pulled into the world
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.73,0:38:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,away from the self.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.55,0:39:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And one's reality
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.65,0:39:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is prior to the self.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.65,0:39:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One's reality is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.73,0:39:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,prior to the self
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.73,0:39:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.44,0:39:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.44,0:39:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.92,0:39:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So your reality is a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.26,0:39:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the innate field
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.26,0:39:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.26,0:39:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,just prior to thinking this,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.15,0:39:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,when you wake up first thing in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.15,0:39:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the field is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.15,0:39:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know who you are yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.42,0:39:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.48,0:39:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.48,0:39:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just the awareness of awareness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.01,0:39:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.01,0:39:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,all you know is that you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.21,0:39:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.21,0:39:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that phase when you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.21,0:39:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you're awake and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.30,0:39:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what the condition is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.94,0:40:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always present.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.38,0:40:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When thinking that I am that which is talking
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.38,0:40:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and thinking is what's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.38,0:40:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The identification of self,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.76,0:40:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of reality as the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.76,0:40:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,when that goes away,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.34,0:40:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.34,0:40:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there's deadening silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.86,0:40:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the question is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.86,0:40:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,how to be in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.86,0:40:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of dead silence
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.96,0:40:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,when the world is talking all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.96,0:40:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.67,0:40:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It took many years to adjust.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.67,0:40:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.73,0:40:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people when they go into that space
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.73,0:40:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,don't readjust.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.73,0:40:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They do not reenter the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.13,0:40:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of karmic momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.80,0:40:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people do return to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.80,0:40:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.03,0:40:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times you're really making an effort
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.03,0:40:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to come out of the state of inner peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.03,0:41:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of like
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.28,0:41:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,having to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.28,0:41:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and deal with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.88,0:41:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look within yourself and see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.88,0:41:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there's really a reluctance
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.88,0:41:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to deal with all this thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.88,0:41:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and judgmentalism
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.13,0:41:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and emotionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.13,0:41:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.32,0:41:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Within yourself you'll find
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.57,0:41:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,man, I'm really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.80,0:41:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everybody here tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.86,0:41:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.86,0:41:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,with dealing with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.86,0:41:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why people look forward
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.76,0:41:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.17,0:41:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait until it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.17,0:41:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It drags on
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.50,0:41:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.50,0:41:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what the end is anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.50,0:41:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.84,0:41:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,An hour later it's all the same, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.84,0:41:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Which brings up the question
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.13,0:41:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,on Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.21,0:41:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody asked me about Alzheimer's
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.34,0:42:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've dealt with Alzheimer's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.34,0:42:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot the last five or ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.34,0:42:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In Alzheimer's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.57,0:42:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the spirit leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.57,0:42:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,starts leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.80,0:42:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.00,0:42:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not really there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.00,0:42:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like an enlightened person.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.05,0:42:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask an enlightened person
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.21,0:42:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,what is today's date?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.21,0:42:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell does he care what today's date is?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.21,0:42:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't live in today's date.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.21,0:42:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no date in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.21,0:42:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.21,0:42:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of nature being what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.21,0:42:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go and ask a tree, I say, what's the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.21,0:42:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't live in the world of dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.30,0:42:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree doesn't live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.11,0:42:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The tragedy of Alzheimer's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.11,0:42:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the witness of Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.65,0:42:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The suffering is in the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.65,0:42:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When you don't know what the hell
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.59,0:42:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the date is anymore, are you suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.59,0:42:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I've asked a thousand Alzheimer's patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.59,0:42:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.01,0:43:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.71,0:43:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that you can't eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.71,0:43:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.71,0:43:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.57,0:43:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what day it is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.57,0:43:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't pay attention to those things anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.69,0:43:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What year were you born?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.53,0:43:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.13,0:43:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they say to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.13,0:43:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What year were you born?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.13,0:43:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.13,0:43:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like asking a woman her age,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.13,0:43:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, 40 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.13,0:43:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You never asked a woman her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.13,0:43:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.13,0:43:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they make up stories
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.13,0:43:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.42,0:43:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you obviously want an answer from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.42,0:43:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so they'll make up a story on the spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.42,0:43:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and five minutes later,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.42,0:43:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,they've forgotten the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.23,0:43:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you fear Alzheimer's?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.23,0:43:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.53,0:43:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people identify
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.11,0:44:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with the content of ego as self,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.11,0:44:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are people
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.36,0:44:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that are frightened to death
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.36,0:44:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of losing their memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.30,0:44:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell if you don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.30,0:44:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,1932 to 1934?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.30,0:44:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so precious
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.30,0:44:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that you want to be able to recall it instantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.30,0:44:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.61,0:44:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A person says,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.61,0:44:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I might lose my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.61,0:44:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.61,0:44:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing better could happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.71,0:44:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Memory is the recall
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.71,0:44:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of perceptual illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.71,0:44:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as it compounded over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.96,0:44:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's like the poison well, folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.96,0:44:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,though it's killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.96,0:44:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do I feel sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.13,0:44:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Alzheimer's patient? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.13,0:44:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the witness, the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.28,0:44:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Two-year-old granny's losing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.28,0:44:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're weeping and sobbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.28,0:44:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is granny weeping and sobbing? No, she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.73,0:44:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it here
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.50,0:45:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in this nursing home?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.50,0:45:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to all the nursing homes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.50,0:45:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Ababai County
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.50,0:45:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,for close to ten years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.50,0:45:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day I knocked my brains out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.50,0:45:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't any other doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.71,0:45:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that would go see them, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.94,0:45:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The county was happy somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.94,0:45:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,would make a house call
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.44,0:45:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and go to the nursing home
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.44,0:45:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.44,0:45:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.76,0:45:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The men and the women
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.76,0:45:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,were all cute as could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.76,0:45:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's because you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.76,0:45:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what's lovable has been
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.09,0:45:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,completely preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.09,0:45:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's lovable is totally there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.17,0:45:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's irrelevant has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.84,0:45:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All they've lost is what's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.84,0:45:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As you get closer to the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.73,0:45:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,some people have,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.73,0:45:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,let's not even title it anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.42,0:45:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the spirit begins to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.42,0:45:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,before the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.44,0:45:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people, by the time
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.44,0:45:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they physically die,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.53,0:46:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the spirit's left years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.53,0:46:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Bill Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.15,0:46:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the founder of AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.15,0:46:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.15,0:46:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and I actually treated him
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.15,0:46:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the last year of his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.15,0:46:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,vitamin E and various stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.15,0:46:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,antioxidants we were fooling around with.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.92,0:46:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would drift off.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.92,0:46:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.21,0:46:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,his watchers would be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.21,0:46:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that Bill had drifted off.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.21,0:46:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it, Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.26,0:46:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.26,0:46:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,there are many places you can go in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.26,0:46:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd been visiting heaven back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.26,0:46:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,like he was shopping for a future resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.26,0:46:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.26,0:46:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see in old people then,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.88,0:46:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,do I fear Alzheimer's in myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.88,0:46:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.90,0:46:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't fear Alzheimer's in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.90,0:46:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.69,0:46:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have senior moments, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.69,0:46:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I call a lot of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.90,0:46:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.90,0:46:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name and what's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.90,0:47:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.90,0:47:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens then
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.53,0:47:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which is important
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.53,0:47:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and significant
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.53,0:47:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer located
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.53,0:47:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,within the ego's functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.03,0:47:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not important to be able to figure out,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.03,0:47:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to read this manual
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.03,0:47:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and figure out how to push all these buttons
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.03,0:47:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I can set the watering system
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.03,0:47:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for every third day
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.61,0:47:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and half time on rain days
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.61,0:47:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and three days on...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.61,0:47:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at one in the store the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.61,0:47:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a new watering system thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.61,0:47:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was mind-boggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.61,0:47:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It has so many bells and whistles
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.61,0:47:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't figure out how the hell
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.61,0:47:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to make it water the lawn, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.15,0:47:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It would serve 12 stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.15,0:47:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you... 12 stations?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.15,0:47:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want one that turns it on and off,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.15,0:47:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.19,0:47:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,On at three, off at four.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.19,0:47:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have one like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.19,0:47:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't have one like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.19,0:47:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.69,0:47:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the easiest way is in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.69,0:48:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,on the way to work you turn the watering system on
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.69,0:48:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and on the way you turn the hose on,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.69,0:48:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the sprinklers, and when you come home
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.69,0:48:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.65,0:48:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that simple or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.75,0:48:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saved you $72.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.23,0:48:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can turn it on and off yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.23,0:48:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.65,0:48:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After breakfast you turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.65,0:48:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Before dinner you turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.21,0:48:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.21,0:48:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so reality then
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.67,0:48:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is the world of simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.50,0:48:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The person with advanced Alzheimer's
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.50,0:48:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is ultra simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.59,0:48:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no needs, no wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.59,0:48:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you say to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.78,0:48:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,how are things here?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.78,0:48:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.82,0:48:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How are they treating you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.94,0:48:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.30,0:48:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather be someplace else?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.73,0:48:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.73,0:48:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're still hanging onto the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.73,0:48:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in the past, you grieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.78,0:49:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But as happily Alzheimer's progresses,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.78,0:49:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose that attachment to the past
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.78,0:49:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you're not grieving
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.78,0:49:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're not living on the farm in Michigan anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.51,0:49:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Except to the witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.51,0:49:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,he is probably closest to enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.57,0:49:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,than most human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.57,0:49:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a statement of fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.67,0:49:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to look at the Alzheimer's patients
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.67,0:49:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.57,0:49:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ, he's a Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.57,0:49:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.57,0:49:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.76,0:49:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.76,0:49:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.80,0:49:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things here yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.80,0:49:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.07,0:49:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.84,0:49:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're living in the instant of now
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.84,0:49:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the self is still present
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.84,0:49:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's only present in the self
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.84,0:49:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.84,0:49:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not present as a small s.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.88,0:49:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Alzheimer's is the dissolution
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.88,0:49:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of the self with a small s
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.09,0:49:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who are more spiritually advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.09,0:50:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,see that the self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.09,0:50:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is still vitally there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.09,0:50:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just as loving, warm, friendly,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.09,0:50:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,responsive in the instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.38,0:50:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we summon forth in Walmart.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.38,0:50:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you lose your
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.38,0:50:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,identification with your persona,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.38,0:50:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just walking with a basket,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.38,0:50:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.38,0:50:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These two nobodies can instantly be
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.38,0:50:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,very friendly and quite loving with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.51,0:50:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.90,0:50:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're walking in Walmart
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.90,0:50:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and somebody bumped into your basket
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.90,0:50:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly she started to cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.90,0:50:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd say to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.90,0:50:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,huh, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.90,0:50:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that veneer that prevents us
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.90,0:50:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from realizing who we are
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.90,0:50:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,has been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.03,0:50:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alzheimer's from a certain viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.03,0:50:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then is a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.42,0:50:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You forget that you're dying
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.42,0:50:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't have to even grieve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.98,0:50:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have Alzheimer's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.98,0:50:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then you've got to worry that you're dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.98,0:50:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got Alzheimer's,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.98,0:50:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't even enter your mind to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.21,0:50:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing is effortless, painless,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.57,0:51:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think on the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.57,0:51:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd hardly notice the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.78,0:51:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you? Could you go on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.78,0:51:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you notice the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.78,0:51:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you notice the body's laying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.88,0:51:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who's gone out of body
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.88,0:51:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,realizes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.88,0:51:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize, oh, where's the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.88,0:51:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's laying there in the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.09,0:51:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.09,0:51:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was still that body.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.36,0:51:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So helpers come to remind you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.36,0:51:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that that isn't yours anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.36,0:51:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.36,0:51:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want it anymore anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.36,0:51:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.36,0:51:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You leave it at 93,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.36,0:51:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,blind, deaf, dumb, crippled,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.36,0:51:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with arthritis and one leg missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.36,0:51:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who's going to hang on to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.38,0:51:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's my view of old age suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.38,0:51:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The suffering is due to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.53,0:51:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,hanging on to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.53,0:51:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.53,0:51:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And the absolute refusal to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.53,0:51:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Death and dying Alzheimer's
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.78,0:51:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,are moments of great opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.78,0:52:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach spiritual enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.59,0:52:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're great moments because
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.59,0:52:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the investment in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.59,0:52:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the investment in the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.59,0:52:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the functions of the body and the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.59,0:52:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,have diminished to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.59,0:52:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's easy to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.17,0:52:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.61,0:52:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To be in the space just prior to thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.61,0:52:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So your reality
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.82,0:52:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is the sense
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.82,0:52:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.17,0:52:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sense of being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.07,0:52:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear what he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.07,0:52:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't necessary to really understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.53,0:52:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You sense that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.09,0:52:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you are present.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.44,0:52:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You sense that you're in the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.44,0:52:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of the allness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.44,0:52:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.88,0:52:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when you walk out in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.88,0:52:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before your stupid mind
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.30,0:52:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,says, isn't that a beautiful tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.30,0:52:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You catch the space in which you saw
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.30,0:52:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a tree's beauty without comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.36,0:53:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the space you live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.01,0:53:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just prior to thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.01,0:53:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to just
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.19,0:53:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,fall back into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.19,0:53:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like something you have to accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.19,0:53:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,through years of study and meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.67,0:53:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to trust it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.67,0:53:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and just drop into that,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.67,0:53:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,back into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.80,0:53:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That is your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.80,0:53:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reality is a priority
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.80,0:53:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to any programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.69,0:53:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reality is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.46,0:53:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what is in the computer world
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.38,0:53:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the software and hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.38,0:53:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your beauty is the hardware
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.38,0:53:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,which is always present.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.30,0:53:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to hitting the button
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.30,0:53:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting the software.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.30,0:53:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that a beautiful tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.30,0:53:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.40,0:53:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, even while you're saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.40,0:53:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you can back off from the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.40,0:53:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and not identify with that statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.44,0:53:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The two things exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.44,0:54:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is both context and content.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.78,0:54:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The two things exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.78,0:54:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One can realize the foolishness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.78,0:54:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the statement
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.80,0:54:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and simultaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.05,0:54:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,be aware of the beauty of the woods
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.05,0:54:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,prior to any comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.05,0:54:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do one or two more questions
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.65,0:54:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll break for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.65,0:54:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to read these is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.05,0:54:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They really have
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.92,0:54:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,very good handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.92,0:54:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like reading the stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.15,0:54:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,on the back of the clock
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.15,0:54:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.86,0:54:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How should we hold the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.86,0:54:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Middle East
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.86,0:54:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,coming back to the present world?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.17,0:54:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The presidency
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.17,0:54:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates around 450
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.17,0:54:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has throughout the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.26,0:54:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a few of them
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.26,0:54:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in olden times
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.26,0:54:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but in modern times
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.40,0:54:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the average consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.40,0:54:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is about 450.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.40,0:55:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Roosevelt was like 499 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.84,0:55:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Churchill was 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.84,0:55:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness then
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.67,0:55:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of the leaders of the modern world
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.67,0:55:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,are usually in the mid-400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.67,0:55:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.67,0:55:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what appeals to reason
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.67,0:55:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.67,0:55:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.94,0:55:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,research,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.94,0:55:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,their advisors.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.94,0:55:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to do what
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.00,0:55:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to pull together
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.00,0:55:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the best advice team
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.00,0:55:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they will give it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.00,0:55:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a slight preference
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.00,0:55:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,due to political position.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.00,0:55:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Current president
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.00,0:55:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,has no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.00,0:55:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with right versus wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.15,0:55:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right is right and wrong is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.15,0:55:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.11,0:55:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Within that context,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.11,0:55:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.11,0:55:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now your question is
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.11,0:55:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,should that context apply?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.53,0:56:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When a tiger is about to rip
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.53,0:56:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,your jugular vein out,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.53,0:56:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the context is a little different
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.73,0:56:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,than looking at a
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.73,0:56:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,tiger in the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.73,0:56:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The context is a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.73,0:56:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's permissible?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.40,0:56:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The alternatives
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.40,0:56:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,are somewhat different
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.61,0:56:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,depending on context.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.61,0:56:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the context of the zoo
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.61,0:56:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes it a little different
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.61,0:56:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,than the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.01,0:56:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.01,0:56:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.90,0:56:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,these are tough ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.17,0:56:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my golly.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.38,0:56:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my golly.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.46,0:56:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We got some really brilliant minds
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.46,0:56:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.98,0:56:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We will answer all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.98,0:56:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.46,0:57:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just answer one more question
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.42,0:57:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we will break for lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.42,0:57:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because these are a lot to sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.42,0:57:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,look at and pull out the essence of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.86,0:57:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot what I was
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.55,0:57:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,going to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.00,0:57:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of questions about
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.00,0:57:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrations of the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.00,0:57:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrating levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.00,0:57:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is only a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.00,0:57:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of getting information.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.13,0:57:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't get you enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.13,0:57:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it does tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.19,0:57:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what's a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.26,0:57:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.26,0:57:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And also what's a pitfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.44,0:57:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What to avoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.61,0:57:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.61,0:57:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.90,0:57:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.73,0:58:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.73,0:58:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell the truth about anything
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.73,0:58:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,instantly brings up a zillion questions
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.01,0:58:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.01,0:58:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to look at the intention
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.01,0:58:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,behind the curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.01,0:58:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,behind the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.48,0:58:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often you find out more
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.48,0:58:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,about what you wanted to know
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.48,0:58:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,by examining the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.46,0:58:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,why the question is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.82,0:58:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a unique opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.82,0:58:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because we've found out
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.82,0:58:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is access
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.01,0:58:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that accounts for
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.01,0:58:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the spin of this photon
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.01,0:58:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.01,0:58:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly the spin of the photon
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.01,0:58:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.01,0:58:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only thing that changed
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.05,0:58:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,was human consciousness observed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.11,0:58:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.11,0:58:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,did nothing but look at this photon.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.26,0:58:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly the photon rotates this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.26,0:58:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This photon rotates this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.26,0:58:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.69,0:58:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No connection between the two whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.69,0:59:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The only connection that's possible
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.26,0:59:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,would be that there's
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.26,0:59:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a field, a field,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.30,0:59:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,common, a matrix,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.30,0:59:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a matrix, a latticework.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.30,0:59:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's called in quantum mechanics
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.30,0:59:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,hypothesized
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.30,0:59:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a matrix,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.61,0:59:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a matrix, a latticework.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.61,0:59:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that under which
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.61,0:59:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.32,0:59:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality of matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.32,0:59:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.32,0:59:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then arises out of that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.32,0:59:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which is invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.32,0:59:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,indefinable, undefinable,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.61,0:59:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.90,0:59:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that sense of that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.90,0:59:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.67,0:59:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of sensing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.67,0:59:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a matter of intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.80,0:59:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You go back within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.80,0:59:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.80,0:59:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there prior to hearing this word.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.80,0:59:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something there
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.34,0:59:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,right before this word
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.34,0:59:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is heard and right before
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.34,1:00:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind thinks of a
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.34,1:00:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,reaction to the word.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.59,1:00:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in that space,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.55,1:00:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the most likely place
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.55,1:00:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and situation
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.21,1:00:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to find that space
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.21,1:00:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that we call enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.21,1:00:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is while you're eating cookies.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.21,1:00:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana's cookies.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.26,1:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If that don't take you there,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.26,1:00:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing will.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.26,1:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll resume then
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.26,1:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in exactly one hour, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.26,1:00:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll do more questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.26,1:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a chance to look at the questions
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.76,1:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,during the break.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.76,1:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well we were asked to test
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.76,1:00:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a number of various things.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.86,1:00:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of them I already know the answer
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.11,1:00:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but just for fun, a near death experience
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.11,1:00:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask that question.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.34,1:00:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.34,1:00:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,correctly phrased right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.38,1:00:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Near death experience
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.38,1:00:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,helps one transcend
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.38,1:00:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the identification with the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.38,1:01:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It can bring about major
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.38,1:01:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,transformations in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.38,1:01:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It can bring about
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.38,1:01:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a major positive leap in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.40,1:01:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you tell out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.40,1:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,from a near death experience
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.40,1:01:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a lot of lack of sophistication
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.40,1:01:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,not only in the general public
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.57,1:01:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but even some spiritual teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.57,1:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of body is one thing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.57,1:01:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,near death experience is another.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.57,1:01:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of body doesn't necessarily
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.57,1:01:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,change your calibratable
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.57,1:01:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.57,1:01:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.57,1:01:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go out of body, come back in body
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.57,1:01:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and boy that was really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.57,1:01:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's really not
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.57,1:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a major shift to consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.92,1:01:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Near death experience
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.92,1:01:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is of a
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.40,1:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,totally different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.38,1:01:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,One is just
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.38,1:01:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,awestruck by the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.46,1:01:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,immensity of the realization
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.46,1:01:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of the nature of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.46,1:01:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.80,1:01:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which you're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.80,1:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is not different than that which
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.80,1:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.15,1:02:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a major transformation
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.15,1:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,near death experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.15,1:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So to tell the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.15,1:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you can calibrate before and after
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.15,1:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.15,1:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of body usually you'll be about the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.15,1:02:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,However out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.15,1:02:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you do become more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.32,1:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You also have an etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.32,1:02:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing that you're quite certain of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.32,1:02:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as you're floating in space
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.32,1:02:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you have an etheric body
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.32,1:02:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because now you're it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.98,1:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of body is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.98,1:02:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of course quite exhilarating.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.98,1:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened to me many years ago
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.01,1:02:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in those days
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.01,1:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing was heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.01,1:02:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've recounted it before.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.01,1:02:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In a serious illness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.01,1:02:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly there I was
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.01,1:02:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,looking down at the body
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.01,1:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in the bed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.09,1:03:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and the interesting thing was
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.09,1:03:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the sense of self
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.09,1:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,went with the etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.46,1:03:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to know
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.46,1:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,feel, think, hear
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.46,1:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,reason, everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.46,1:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of I was up here
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.46,1:03:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.01,1:03:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is an opportunity
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.01,1:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.01,1:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that the sense of self
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.01,1:03:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual self
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.36,1:03:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is an energy body and not a physical body.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.36,1:03:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.42,1:03:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it had any
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.42,1:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly transformative experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.42,1:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told my psychoanalyst
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.61,1:03:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,about it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.90,1:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in psychoanalysis at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.90,1:03:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I bless him, dear Dr. Oversee
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.90,1:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I said
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.90,1:03:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,God almighty there was this experience
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.90,1:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what you had a toxic psychosis there
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.90,1:03:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with a duplication of the body image
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.90,1:03:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and a rejection of one aspect of it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.90,1:03:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.90,1:03:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you're right, you're right
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.90,1:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we were both atheists
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.19,1:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't think much of
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.19,1:04:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,God and religion and at the time
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.19,1:04:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't either so
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.19,1:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't have any problem with it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.19,1:04:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a toxic
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.21,1:04:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,couple of irritated brain cells
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.21,1:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all we knew about in those days.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.26,1:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright we've got some interesting
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.26,1:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,leading questions into the subject
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.26,1:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,which we're going to go into anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.21,1:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In my talking about women of course
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.21,1:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,just using Mother's Day
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.21,1:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as a point of reference
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.28,1:04:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not differentiating
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.28,1:04:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,men from women because
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.28,1:04:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity of course is equally
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.28,1:04:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,present
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.53,1:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the form that it takes within the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.53,1:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,perceptual world is different
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.53,1:04:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean a man is different from a woman
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.53,1:04:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,within the physical world
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.53,1:04:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and symbolically
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.53,1:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they represent
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.53,1:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,symbolically in the unconscious
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.53,1:04:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,those of you who are
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.53,1:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,familiar with the work
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.53,1:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of Jung and all
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.53,1:05:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,realize that the archetype of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.53,1:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the feminine and the archetype of the male
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.53,1:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,are two different things and historically
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.53,1:05:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they've always been
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.53,1:05:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,even the planets are named with various
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.53,1:05:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,genders and the gods and all
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.38,1:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that's really a different subject
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.40,1:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a subject
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.26,1:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of study in itself
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.26,1:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the origin of how this arises
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.26,1:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,how it expresses itself
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.26,1:05:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.42,1:05:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of all is the same of course
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.42,1:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.42,1:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,its expression
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.42,1:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as a woman
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.42,1:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and then using that
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.42,1:05:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to denote the importance of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.57,1:05:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,context, how woman was conceived of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.57,1:05:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in the 1800s
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.57,1:05:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,early 1900s now
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.57,1:05:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is a shift of context
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.73,1:05:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but the reality of course
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.73,1:05:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,has not been changed at all
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.73,1:06:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,some of these
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.73,1:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,are a little too complicated
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.73,1:06:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer them
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.73,1:06:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,they're beyond me
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.73,1:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,all right
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.94,1:06:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my notes about them
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.38,1:06:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,here we have
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.38,1:06:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we forgot to put this up before
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.38,1:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just a point of reference
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.38,1:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a very useful point of reference
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.38,1:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because I get many requests
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.38,1:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from all kinds of groups
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.38,1:06:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,publishers, writers and all
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.38,1:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to reproduce it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.38,1:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I always tell them yes
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.38,1:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's useful
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.44,1:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as a teaching
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.44,1:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,teaching device
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.44,1:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.57,1:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,people say well
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.80,1:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,see people can't seem to get out of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.80,1:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego's
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.80,1:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,view of things being better
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.80,1:06:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,than others or ranking them
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.80,1:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is there
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.98,1:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is 500 better than 400
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.98,1:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,no, 500 is a different
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.98,1:06:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,different problem than 400
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.98,1:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to have any calibrated
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.17,1:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,number at all indicates a problem
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.46,1:07:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're at 500 your problem is
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.46,1:07:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,600
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.53,1:07:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,things aren't better than others
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.53,1:07:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,they're just different than others
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.65,1:07:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,people that are just entering the 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.65,1:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,are trying to
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.30,1:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,own the capacity of reason
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.30,1:07:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and logic and all
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.36,1:07:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is what we call
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.36,1:07:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,sophomoric is usually something
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.36,1:07:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody that's just entered the 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.36,1:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're dazzled by their capacity
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.36,1:07:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to use logic and thinking
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.48,1:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.48,1:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because they don't realize its downside
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.48,1:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they take it to the ridiculous extreme
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.48,1:07:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.09,1:07:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they write
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.09,1:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,legislation
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.09,1:07:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's okay
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.09,1:07:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the abstract but you should try to live
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.09,1:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,with it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.57,1:08:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I read somewhere that the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.57,1:08:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the IRS regs run
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.57,1:08:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,58,000 pages and of course
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.57,1:08:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you know as a taxpayer
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.57,1:08:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you are legally liable
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.57,1:08:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for knowing all of its contents
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.57,1:08:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.57,1:08:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.57,1:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's unknowable the government can't
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.57,1:08:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,understand it so it makes you responsible
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.57,1:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for knowing it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.06,1:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so I mean that's the intellect gone wild
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.06,1:08:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without any limitation
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.06,1:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so ranking would be then
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.06,1:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind's
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.22,1:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,proclivity for status
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.22,1:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and things like this and then projecting it onto
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.22,1:08:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,these fields
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.25,1:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing is better than anything else
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.25,1:08:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it's different than
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.34,1:08:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,something else because it's addressing
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.34,1:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole different problem
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.50,1:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's addressing a whole different problem
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.50,1:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is loss
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.35,1:08:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the occasion for grief
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.31,1:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.43,1:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the gateway to freedom and elation
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.88,1:09:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on who you lost eh
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.42,1:09:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.64,1:09:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so you see you don't have
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.64,1:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to mourn loss at all
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.64,1:09:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see that
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.73,1:09:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,loss is the occasion
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.31,1:09:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you know let's say you own a whole head of
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.31,1:09:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,cattle and they're all dead by morning
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.31,1:09:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,terrible disease
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.69,1:09:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,well you don't have to get up and milk them
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.69,1:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you that
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.97,1:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,four o'clock in the morning in the midwest
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.97,1:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,through the snow and the ice and pitch blackness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.97,1:09:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,with snow up to here
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.07,1:09:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and walk through all that cattle poo
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.07,1:09:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to milk this thing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.68,1:09:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.89,1:09:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so every loss then
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.89,1:09:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,can be recontextualized
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.89,1:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as an opportunity for freedom
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.89,1:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as valuable as that
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.89,1:09:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,position may have been
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.89,1:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it still is the opportunity now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.89,1:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to discover a new life
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.89,1:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the company collapses
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.38,1:10:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose your position
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.38,1:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is that a loss
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.38,1:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it is only if you hang on to the past
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.34,1:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what is really going on
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.34,1:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is you're afraid of the freedom
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.36,1:10:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that the dissolution of that commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.36,1:10:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,now opens up
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.36,1:10:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you're now free to become anything you want
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.36,1:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,go anywhere you want
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.14,1:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going to stay in the same part of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.14,1:10:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,same part of the country
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.26,1:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words it's sort of scary
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.26,1:10:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the freedom that you had
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.26,1:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.46,1:10:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ranking then would be just a projection
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.46,1:10:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that we project onto this
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.46,1:10:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the question often arises
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.48,1:10:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you see perfection
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.48,1:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in any and all conditions
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.64,1:10:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because perception is a projection
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.64,1:10:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.64,1:10:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you will find what you're looking for
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.64,1:10:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the whole basis of
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.64,1:10:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,quantum mechanics
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.64,1:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason they stop calling things measurements
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.64,1:11:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is because
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.25,1:11:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what is found is
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.07,1:11:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the consequence of what you're looking for
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.07,1:11:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the observed is
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.81,1:11:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,then seen as a function
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.81,1:11:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of the observer
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.14,1:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the observer
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.73,1:11:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the observer is what determines
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.73,1:11:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,what's observed
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.81,1:11:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,now what's observed
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.61,1:11:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what's observed
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.61,1:11:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on intention
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.77,1:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we said that calibrated level
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.77,1:11:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.77,1:11:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as karma has to do with
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.77,1:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual intention
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.26,1:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,now spiritual intention doesn't
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.26,1:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,fluctuate
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.30,1:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it tends to move quite slowly
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.30,1:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,although you can have a major event
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.30,1:11:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,such as a near death experience
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.30,1:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or a spiritual intention
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.30,1:11:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly takes a giant leap
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.68,1:11:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment to moment
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.68,1:11:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,little angriness, irritation, regrets
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.68,1:11:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,all these things
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.68,1:12:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,those are not fluctuations on the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.68,1:12:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness is pretty steady
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.89,1:12:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's set up by the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.89,1:12:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.89,1:12:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic development
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.89,1:12:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.93,1:12:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,your spiritual commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.07,1:12:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so the spiritual commitment then
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.07,1:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to prevail
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.07,1:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,fluctuations may occur
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.21,1:12:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,only in a fleeting thought
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.21,1:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you calibrated a thought
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.21,1:12:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the thoughts may jump all over
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.23,1:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.23,1:12:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't change that easily
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.23,1:12:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and people involved in spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.23,1:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,know
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.27,1:12:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,how difficult that is
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.27,1:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to get it to change
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.27,1:12:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.27,1:12:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it's pretty much set
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.27,1:12:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and determined
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.27,1:12:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,how you see the world
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.97,1:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrated level of energy
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.97,1:12:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is influenced
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.97,1:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then through your own decision
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.06,1:12:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is it influenced by the group
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.06,1:12:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.39,1:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.13,1:13:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrated a level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.13,1:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is influenced by the group
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.13,1:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with which you identify
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.13,1:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.13,1:13:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it is influenced
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.13,1:13:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are saying
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.13,1:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that as my reality
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.13,1:13:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so it isn't so much the group
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.13,1:13:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.35,1:13:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,are verifying that the group
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.35,1:13:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,represents your own
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.42,1:13:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual goal
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.42,1:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,not killing innocent children
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.11,1:13:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,may be a very important
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.11,1:13:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual learning down here
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.11,1:13:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,there are certain very large
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.11,1:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,religious groups in the world right now
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.11,1:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,where getting up this far
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.11,1:13:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is a great advance
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.22,1:13:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,getting over 70
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.22,1:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is a major improvement
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.65,1:13:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that God is not pleased by your
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.65,1:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,killing thousands of innocent women and children
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.65,1:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,would seem so
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.81,1:13:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,ludicrous to us
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.81,1:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but it might be a tremendous
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.81,1:13:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,aha to somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.07,1:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so as you move up
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.07,1:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,your own spiritual awareness moves up
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.07,1:14:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the group that you find useful at one time
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.07,1:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you are going to outgrow the group
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.34,1:14:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually you outgrow all groups
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.34,1:14:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so the group is useful
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.02,1:14:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,as mutual support
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.02,1:14:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.02,1:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,continuous feedback
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.02,1:14:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,helps to clarify one's understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.02,1:14:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of that particular religious position
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.02,1:14:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or spiritual position
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.31,1:14:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and then one moves on
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.31,1:14:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we spoke
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.73,1:14:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,there were a number of different groups
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.73,1:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,people asked me about individually
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.73,1:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like to do them publicly
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.93,1:14:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you see by their fruits you shall know them
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.93,1:14:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have to ask what
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.55,1:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.22,1:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrated level of certain
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.22,1:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,groups and their actions
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.22,1:14:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.47,1:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,by their fruits you shall know them
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.77,1:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so we did write something about
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.77,1:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the difference between a true spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.77,1:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,group and a cult
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.77,1:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,cults calibrate below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.77,1:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the quickest way
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.77,1:15:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a cult is non-integrist
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.77,1:15:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so a cult may take the name
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.77,1:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of a great leader or avatar
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.77,1:15:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or spiritual guru or whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.77,1:15:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and call itself that
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.77,1:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and then underneath the guise of that
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.77,1:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,really become a political action
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.77,1:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,group
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.18,1:15:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the one in China that's having trouble
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.47,1:15:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,with the government you see
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.47,1:15:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,its problem is
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.47,1:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that it didn't stick to just
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.47,1:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,strictly spiritual it got political
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.47,1:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,when it got political
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.47,1:15:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it began to challenge the Chinese authority
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.47,1:15:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,all governments
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.47,1:15:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,by nature protect themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.47,1:15:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why they're your government
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.47,1:15:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so China
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.47,1:15:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,outlawed them right
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.47,1:15:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Falun Gong I think is the name of it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.47,1:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you stay home and meditate
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.47,1:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and do good works the government will not take
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.47,1:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a position about you
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.47,1:15:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you start getting out there with the parade
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.47,1:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're going to overthrow the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.47,1:16:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,regime and put in your
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.47,1:16:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,philosophical concepts
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.47,1:16:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,prepare to die
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.47,1:16:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you know prepare to die
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.56,1:16:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you can make a grandstand statement
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.56,1:16:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but that isn't what makes the world
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.56,1:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,turn you know what I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.06,1:16:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so a cult can take on the name of a great
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.06,1:16:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,leader call itself
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.06,1:16:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you know the holy church
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.06,1:16:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of God and
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.14,1:16:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the holy church of God
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.68,1:16:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the name of the holy church of God
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.68,1:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,burned down the homes
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.68,1:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.68,1:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.68,1:16:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,just because they call themselves that doesn't mean anything
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.68,1:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so we define
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.68,1:16:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the difference between a cult and a truly
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.68,1:16:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,integrative spiritual group
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.68,1:16:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of course we as a group know all you have to do
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.68,1:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is calibrate them
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.68,1:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but to the world
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.86,1:16:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is of God
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.86,1:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,gives forth love and peace
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.86,1:16:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's as simple as that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.86,1:16:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,love and peace is what radiates from it
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.77,1:17:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes that
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.77,1:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes the original of the spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.77,1:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the originator or the original speaker
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.77,1:17:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of that spiritual truth
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.77,1:17:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it is loving and pure
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.77,1:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but then that's grabbed by other groups
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.77,1:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,who then run with it
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.77,1:17:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and use it as justification
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.77,1:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.89,1:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,convert people by the sword
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.02,1:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus meant the sword of truth right
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.02,1:17:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't mean
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.11,1:17:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the sword of steel
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.14,1:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's misused
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.14,1:17:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,then for other ends
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.81,1:17:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,we notice
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.69,1:17:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that people are born
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.69,1:17:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,at different levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.69,1:17:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the very instant of birth
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.69,1:17:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's another question having to do
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.69,1:17:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with geography I meant today
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.69,1:17:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to have a transparency
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.69,1:17:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to project with the world map
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.69,1:17:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,showing calibrating the various
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.82,1:18:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.82,1:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and prevailing civilizations
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.82,1:18:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,over the world
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.82,1:18:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very interesting
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.82,1:18:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.27,1:18:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that like
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.78,1:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,light
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.78,1:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to attract light
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.78,1:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that's sort of true
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.78,1:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you're born with a
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.89,1:18:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness of
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.07,1:18:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,50 let's say
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.07,1:18:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you're very likely to get
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.59,1:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,born into a body
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.59,1:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that happens to be part of a civilization
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.59,1:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,civilization
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.59,1:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that in general
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.59,1:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates around 50
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.68,1:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.68,1:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like nothing happens by accident
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.81,1:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that if light
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.81,1:18:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,light tends to go to light
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.89,1:18:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,at the very moment of birth
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.89,1:18:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,at the very moment
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.89,1:18:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,before birth even
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.89,1:18:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.89,1:19:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the entity is already
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.89,1:19:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,identifiable
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.89,1:19:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we can actually calibrate it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.39,1:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,what we just said is true
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.39,1:19:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.86,1:19:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done it over and over
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.46,1:19:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so what we think is
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.46,1:19:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,unspiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.57,1:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say we look at the lifestyle
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.57,1:19:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of somebody here
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.57,1:19:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and we go cluck cluck cluck
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.57,1:19:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah but that person came in
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.57,1:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,here for them to be
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.86,1:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,at 100 or 150 is a major
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.86,1:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,advance
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.86,1:19:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you can look
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.97,1:19:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,back at previous lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.97,1:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and these
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.26,1:19:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,areas that you transcend
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.26,1:19:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,become very
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.82,1:19:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,important
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.82,1:19:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you stand out of that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.93,1:19:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.93,1:19:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the lifetime of surmounting
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.25,1:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,physical death
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.25,1:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's thrilling
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.78,1:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you commit harry carry
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.78,1:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and ecstasy
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.18,1:20:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the second you're out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.21,1:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstasy
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.21,1:20:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,surmounted that for all time
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.56,1:20:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,never again
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.56,1:20:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to be inhibited by the fear of physical death
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.19,1:20:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes a very ferocious warrior
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.55,1:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,who's not afraid of death
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.55,1:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the fearless warrior
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.55,1:20:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you can walk into a hail of bullets
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.55,1:20:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't give a rap about it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.78,1:20:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you're no longer susceptible to that
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.78,1:20:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,well now you've transcended that level
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.78,1:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point to
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.21,1:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,i don't have to get myself killed over and over
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.21,1:20:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to get the point
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.21,1:20:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you got a physical body
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.21,1:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the thing laying there
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.21,1:20:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the other spirit and you laugh at each other
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.21,1:20:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,great job joe great job
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.21,1:20:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we both did it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.21,1:20:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's really no point to do that again
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.21,1:20:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to commit harry carry 10 or 12 times
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.21,1:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the point of it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.27,1:20:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not pleasant
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.27,1:20:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so i'd only do it once
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.27,1:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if i were you
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.75,1:21:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't that one thing is better than another
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.65,1:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.64,1:21:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as you grasp the totality
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.64,1:21:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.64,1:21:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as it has evolved throughout time
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.64,1:21:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way it manifests
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.73,1:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,on this planet
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.73,1:21:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as the evolution of life on this planet
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.73,1:21:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,evolving into mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.73,1:21:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,evolving into modern man
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.73,1:21:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to realize
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.57,1:21:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're dealing with
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.94,1:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you're dealing with
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.27,1:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,like a profound morass
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.27,1:21:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which consciousness is only
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.27,1:21:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,just barely popping it's little head
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.27,1:21:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't cross 200
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.30,1:21:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,until the late 1980s
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.30,1:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.30,1:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.30,1:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,modern consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.46,1:21:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is just being born now
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.46,1:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we're probably part of the birth process
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.81,1:21:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.81,1:21:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,homo spiritus
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.53,1:22:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and so
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.53,1:22:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,homo spiritus is
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.89,1:22:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a declaration made by
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.89,1:22:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,this great wonderful being here
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.57,1:22:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,homo spiritus is correct
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.57,1:22:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it is the emergence of homo spiritus
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.57,1:22:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.57,1:22:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in the book i
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.57,1:22:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,then i say
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.57,1:22:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,there is now
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.67,1:22:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,emerging out of this morass
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.67,1:22:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of negativity
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.67,1:22:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ignorance
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.67,1:22:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally the 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.85,1:22:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.85,1:22:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the appearance of love which is relatively recent in the human condition
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.85,1:22:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as a prevailing
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.85,1:22:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,energy
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.14,1:22:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we have now the emergence
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.14,1:22:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of the spiritually aware being
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.14,1:22:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,aware of himself
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.14,1:22:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as a spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.34,1:22:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the emergence of homo
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.34,1:22:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritus
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.01,1:22:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,all the branches off the evolutionary tree
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.01,1:22:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,see
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.01,1:23:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not a linear thing
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.01,1:23:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,where this gets better and better and better and better
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.01,1:23:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in the evolutionary tree
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.01,1:23:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution by the way happens on the level of
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.01,1:23:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness then it manifests within
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.01,1:23:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical domain
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.19,1:23:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but you see it's branches off the tree
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.19,1:23:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,this tree this branch goes off here
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.19,1:23:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,this branch doesn't just get longer
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.19,1:23:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and bigger and better
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.19,1:23:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,no it stops there
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.42,1:23:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's potentiality has been realized
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.42,1:23:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when it hits the perfection of that which it is
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.42,1:23:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you see
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.84,1:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,later another branch off the tree
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.84,1:23:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and then another branch higher
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.89,1:23:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,off the tree
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.89,1:23:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the one branch doesn't
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.13,1:23:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.13,1:23:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,as it's expressed in
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.13,1:23:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind is not
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.13,1:23:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the continuous evolution of one
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.13,1:23:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,trend at all
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.13,1:23:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the emergence of a new trend
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.13,1:23:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a new trend
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.81,1:23:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,those of us here today represent really
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.81,1:23:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a new branch off the evolutionary tree
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.81,1:24:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we are not an improvement
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.81,1:24:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on Cro-Magnon man
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.34,1:24:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not an improvement
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.34,1:24:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not an improvement on homo erectus
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.34,1:24:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,homo erectus went here
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.34,1:24:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and he got as far as homo erectus could go
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.34,1:24:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,end of homo erectus
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.34,1:24:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,each of us then represents
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.81,1:24:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we have
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.81,1:24:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a branch off the tree
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.81,1:24:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a new branch off the tree
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.81,1:24:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,called homo spiritus
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.43,1:24:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.89,1:24:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's so
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.28,1:24:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the group here
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.64,1:24:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly represents
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.64,1:24:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is homo spiritus
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.64,1:24:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness that we're more than
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.64,1:24:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a physicality
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.64,1:24:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness that we're more than a mind
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.72,1:24:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the recognition of
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.72,1:24:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual potential within
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.72,1:24:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to be discovered and nurtured
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.72,1:24:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,for it to flourish and blossom
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.72,1:24:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,did the enderthal man
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.98,1:25:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,worry about these things?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.98,1:25:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.98,1:25:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,not suitable
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.10,1:25:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Cro-Magnon man
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.10,1:25:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,was about 70
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.81,1:25:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that has to do with physical survival as an animal
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.80,1:25:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,good enough to eat, to mate
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.80,1:25:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay alive
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.14,1:25:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's the animal
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.14,1:25:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so he had to first perfect
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.35,1:25:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the ability to maintain life
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.35,1:25:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,within animal form
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.35,1:25:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,within biped form
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.35,1:25:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and then consciousness went on
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.35,1:25:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness got bored with that one
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.35,1:25:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,got bored with him
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.48,1:25:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,said he's boring
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.48,1:25:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and went on and developed this Cro-Magnon
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.48,1:25:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and then on through the ages
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.84,1:25:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what we see now
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.96,1:25:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is where the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.96,1:25:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is at its present moment
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.96,1:25:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,this moment here
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.43,1:25:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.43,1:26:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.43,1:26:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout eons and eons
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.65,1:26:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of time
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.50,1:26:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,has resulted
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.75,1:26:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in us
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.75,1:26:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we're it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.75,1:26:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we are it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.77,1:26:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,amen
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.77,1:26:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we are it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.77,1:26:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we are it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.77,1:26:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the advancing edge of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.77,1:26:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is really what is here today
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.77,1:26:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.89,1:26:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the ultimate truth
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.89,1:26:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,how does one reach it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.89,1:26:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the tools that are useful for the task
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.89,1:26:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,or the advancing edge of spiritual consciousness is
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.89,1:26:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.47,1:26:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is it possible
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.47,1:26:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in the old religions
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.47,1:26:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,well religion is one thing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.69,1:26:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual truth is another
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.32,1:26:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,hypothetically at least in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.32,1:26:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,they are one and the same
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.32,1:26:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but we see throughout history
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.32,1:26:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,how spiritual truth then gets destroyed
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.32,1:27:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for secular means
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.32,1:27:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the original truth is lost within
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.32,1:27:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the more spiritually
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.10,1:27:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced person utilizes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.10,1:27:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,what they realize
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.10,1:27:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual truth from that religion
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.10,1:27:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and lets the shaft go
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.10,1:27:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,lets the shaft go
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.10,1:27:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you eat meat on Friday or not
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.10,1:27:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is really irrelevant to God
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.34,1:27:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see if that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.36,1:27:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.59,1:27:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,ok
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.65,1:27:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,when I grew up you didn't eat meat on Friday
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.65,1:27:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was respectful
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.65,1:27:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,well no it was a sin
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.65,1:27:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it was worse than respectful
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.65,1:27:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,high episcopal it was like catholic
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.65,1:27:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway you didn't eat meat on Friday
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.88,1:27:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it was really out of respect
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.88,1:27:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for the religion
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.88,1:27:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and respect for the teaching
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.88,1:27:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it got you in or out of heaven
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.88,1:27:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.88,1:27:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but as a kid I suppose I would worry
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.88,1:27:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ate meat on a Friday and died
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.88,1:27:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd think you were going to the other place
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.88,1:27:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to do some
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.88,1:27:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,public leaders resist
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.88,1:28:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that are in the middle east resist
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.03,1:28:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself have wondered about
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.03,1:28:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,this particular individual
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.03,1:28:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to calibrate him in public
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.03,1:28:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he resists
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.03,1:28:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he's on TV every night so I guess he's not too timid
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.03,1:28:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,this gentleman
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.03,1:28:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates over 200 resist
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.03,1:28:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,wow over 220
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.42,1:28:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,230
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.64,1:28:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,240 wow 260
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.64,1:28:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,250
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.35,1:28:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Arafat 250
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.44,1:28:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see Arafat was
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.44,1:28:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,at 250
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.44,1:28:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,10 years ago resisted
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.44,1:28:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,no now Arafat is
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.44,1:28:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,interesting because we see a lot of
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.44,1:28:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,well known in fact currently popular
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.44,1:28:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,gurus that wrote
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.44,1:28:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,books years ago when they were in a high space
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.44,1:28:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,usually in the mid 500s
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.44,1:28:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and their books calibrate in high 500s
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.44,1:28:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you calibrate what is the energy of this
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.44,1:28:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,entity today you'll often find
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.44,1:28:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,they're like 130 common
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.27,1:28:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,very big name gurus in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.27,1:28:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody goes oh when you mention their name
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.27,1:29:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrate them to like 140
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.27,1:29:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or something you know
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.97,1:29:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because they went up
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.06,1:29:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and then were hit by
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.06,1:29:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say their opposite
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.06,1:29:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and succumbed to the opposite
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.57,1:29:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that's how the cult is born
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.57,1:29:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have a certain charisma
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.57,1:29:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,when people start to follow you
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.57,1:29:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you start to believe your own publicity
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.57,1:29:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you start getting power over others
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.57,1:29:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you start telling them what to do
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.57,1:29:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you develop a cult
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.57,1:29:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to swear an oath
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.57,1:29:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you gotta pay money
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.57,1:29:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,get a thing on your whatchamacallit
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.64,1:29:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.64,1:29:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,every time the name of the leader
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.64,1:29:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you bow
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.15,1:29:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,even Est
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.15,1:29:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless Est
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.15,1:29:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it was Werner right
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.15,1:29:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it was Werner everything
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.15,1:29:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,bigger than a movie theater
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.15,1:29:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,on the screen
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.15,1:29:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it was all Werner
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.15,1:29:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other hand Est taught some
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.15,1:29:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,terrific things
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.35,1:29:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,with Est you can take off weight very easy
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.35,1:30:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.35,1:30:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,lots of good things in it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.35,1:30:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.38,1:30:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so then the cult we see
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.38,1:30:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody asked me about various things
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.38,1:30:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I don't want to calibrate them in public
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.89,1:30:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the leader becomes charismatic in a cult
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.02,1:30:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes all Baba so and so
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.02,1:30:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,master so and so
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.02,1:30:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,master Baba
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.50,1:30:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so it all becomes all master Baba
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.50,1:30:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with many oohs and ahhs
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.50,1:30:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's like a personality cult
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.50,1:30:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's a
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.85,1:30:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,a specialness to belonging
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.85,1:30:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to the group
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.85,1:30:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a group form that gets a name
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.85,1:30:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe an initiation ceremony
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.10,1:30:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.10,1:30:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,now the group becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.59,1:30:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you're either with them or not with them
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.61,1:30:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.61,1:30:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you're one of us or not one of us
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.61,1:30:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so it becomes very
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.77,1:30:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of seeing yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.42,1:30:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as part of the all
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.42,1:30:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the allness of life
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.42,1:30:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you now become partitioned as special
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.42,1:31:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,special
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.55,1:31:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're a member that makes you special
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.55,1:31:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's group lingo
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.55,1:31:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,which is only known to the members of the group
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.55,1:31:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the specialness of the cult leader
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.55,1:31:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a negative
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.69,1:31:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,reaction if you leave
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.69,1:31:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if you decide you're going to leave
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.69,1:31:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the holy
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.22,1:31:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,rosary of the round table
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.22,1:31:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.22,1:31:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,horrible things happen to you
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.22,1:31:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,snakes in your mailbox
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.22,1:31:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,hate mail
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.22,1:31:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's a negative reaction
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.27,1:31:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,if you try to leave
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.27,1:31:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so you like become a prisoner
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.27,1:31:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so the brainwashing
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.27,1:31:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,what is really brainwashing
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.27,1:31:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is then proceeded about this organization
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.27,1:31:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,about its specialness
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.27,1:31:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,often it considers itself exclusive
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.27,1:31:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,some go so far as to say
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.63,1:31:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're the only ones
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.63,1:31:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that are going to get into heaven
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.72,1:31:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you know it's a little hard to imagine
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.72,1:31:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people are going to believe that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.81,1:31:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's a specialness
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.81,1:31:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a uniqueness
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.81,1:32:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a cult-like atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.81,1:32:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a specialness to belonging
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.81,1:32:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,or not belonging
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.81,1:32:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,various titles go with it
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.90,1:32:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and after a while
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.17,1:32:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,there's probably a lot to be learned
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.17,1:32:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a lot to be learned
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.48,1:32:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at that level
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.48,1:32:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but then at a certain level
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.48,1:32:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to realize
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.48,1:32:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this is not freeing and liberating
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.48,1:32:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this is confining
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.48,1:32:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this is totalitarian
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.48,1:32:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at its greatest expression
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.48,1:32:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes totalitarian
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.48,1:32:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at that point your intuition will tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.48,1:32:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it's time to move on
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.97,1:32:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very often hard to see
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.97,1:32:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.97,1:32:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the adulation
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.97,1:32:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with which certain people
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.97,1:32:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are held by large groups
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.02,1:32:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so mass hysteria
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.02,1:32:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the suggestion of madness of crowds
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.02,1:32:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,takes over
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.02,1:32:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you're in a group
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.02,1:32:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody's going
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.28,1:32:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the charisma of the leader then
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.28,1:32:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes magnetic
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.28,1:33:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and the adulation of the group
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.28,1:33:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to be infectious
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.28,1:33:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so you've got to watch
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.28,1:33:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that you don't get brainwashed
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.31,1:33:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing a teacher can do
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.31,1:33:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is reflect truth
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.31,1:33:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't make them special, unique
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.31,1:33:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,anything at all
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.31,1:33:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget to a realized person
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.31,1:33:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,their condition is just nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.31,1:33:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just the way it is
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.31,1:33:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is a cat's condition to a cat special?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.31,1:33:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,no, it's just being a cat
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.44,1:33:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.69,1:33:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a true teacher is just like a cat
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.69,1:33:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it just is what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.69,1:33:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing to say about that
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.69,1:33:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just being what one is
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.69,1:33:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.93,1:33:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so there would hardly be any
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.93,1:33:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,adulation expected from being what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.93,1:33:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the cat doesn't expect me to say
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.93,1:33:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,oh great cat
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.93,1:33:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are a cat
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.93,1:33:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence within is so powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.93,1:33:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it is of itself
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.93,1:33:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it is of itself
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.93,1:33:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it bypasses all personhood
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.93,1:33:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so there is no one to
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.93,1:34:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,go ooh and ahh over
